'''2017年世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛'''是第18届[[世界速度滑冰锦标赛|世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛]]，于2017年2月9日至12日在韩国江陵速度滑冰馆进行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.isu.org/media/419577/announcement-isu-world-single-distances-ss-champs-2017-gangneung.pdf |title=ISU World Single Distances Speed Skating Championships 2017, Gangneung, Korea - Announcement |publisher=[[国际滑冰联盟|International Skating Union]] |access-date=2017-01-28 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202235352/http://static.isu.org/media/419577/announcement-isu-world-single-distances-ss-champs-2017-gangneung.pdf |archive-date=2017-02-02}}</ref>。此次比赛是江陵速度滑冰馆完工后举办的首场国际比赛，同时也是[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2018年平昌冬奥]][[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会速度滑冰比赛|速度滑冰项目]]的测试赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1046786/gangneung-oval-prepares-to-stage-isu-world-single-distances-speed-skating-championships|title=Gangneung Oval prepares to stage ISU World Single Distances Speed Skating Championships|work=Inside the Games|date=2017-02-08|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313020459/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1046786/gangneung-oval-prepares-to-stage-isu-world-single-distances-speed-skating-championships|archivedate=2017-03-13}}</ref>。

